task.summary: before arranging code for list. Working version for list
- fixed bug with emails - now an email must respect the mail format, not just be between tags "<>" - fixed bug with textStyle - added LaTex package asmfonts, for an extented set of fonts used in math

- added support for greek characters - now can be printed in their raw form - code - used tcblistings in place of minted(and verbatim) - allows to print code in tcolorboxes that is formatted ok - break the line in case it exceeds the \textwidth - special chars(accents and greek letters) are excaped with && - moved all footnotes to last page (this way tcoloboxes inside tcolorboxes did not crash) -Unformatted - \verb is not used anymore because it does not work inside other envs(that is widely used) - now the chars are printed as they are, and latex special chars are escaped
